{"tid":1474781,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"開始覺得好累，好想放棄","createTime":"2019-08-15T09:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T10:16:20.000Z","uid":187995,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9ea08c067580b32fa2171422700cb6a9c10543e3","tid":1474781,"uid":187995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"一開始同幾個朋友一齊踏上旅程<br />\n最初我行得比較慢<br />\n佢哋會等埋我，鼓勵我行快啲<br />\n然後開始有人因為做法唔同而分開行<br />\n我都明白兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n之後我行得比較快，本來想鼓勵佢地<br />\n但佢地話：「你行先啦，我地行唔到咁快。」<br />\n我認為佢地會喺背後支持我，所以獨自行咗一段時間<br />\n我回頭一望，發現佢地叫我自己行個陣已經停低咗<br />\n我大叫，但佢地已被無力感操控，冇辦法再行<br />\n開頭分道揚鑣嘅朋友亦行得越來越遠<br />\n最後我只能一個人行落去<br />\n<br />\n但近期我開始失去動力，開始慢慢行，有停低嘅想法<br />\n<br />\n求鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ba20ff78715d561e3ee3b6a04d45f9226286f6","tid":1474781,"uid":31705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:48:01.000Z","msg":"我地大把兄弟仲企響前面頂緊 我地唔頂 香港就無"},{"pid":"7fb641f78a676d00e383f5607613c71648af41b1","tid":1474781,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:51:06.000Z","msg":"休息完再起行 每個人都有攰既一刻<br />\n但不放棄"},{"pid":"738e41c044a550869d1e0d629cb88e65024b91ed","tid":1474781,"uid":301633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:51:48.000Z","msg":"巴打絲打齊撐你!無力感我都有，就靠巴打絲打嘅支持。"},{"pid":"541b0d2d8b2c0eb110d16560da635c74b9256461","tid":1474781,"uid":253954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ea08c067580b32fa2171422700cb6a9c10543e3","tid":1474781,"uid":187995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"一開始同幾個朋友一齊踏上旅程<br />\n最初我行得比較慢<br />\n佢哋會等埋我，鼓勵我行快啲<br />\n然後開始有人因為做法唔同而分開行<br />\n我都明白兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n之後我行得比較快，本來想鼓勵佢地<br />\n但佢地話：「你行先啦，我地行唔到咁快。」<br />\n我認為佢地會喺背後支持我，所以獨自行咗一段時間<br />\n我回頭一望，發現佢地叫我自己行個陣已經停低咗<br />\n我大叫，但佢地已被無力感操控，冇辦法再行<br />\n開頭分道揚鑣嘅朋友亦行得越來越遠<br />\n最後我只能一個人行落去<br />\n<br />\n但近期我開始失去動力，開始慢慢行，有停低嘅想法<br />\n<br />\n求鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:53:46.000Z","msg":"慢慢黎,休息下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電話都要叉電啦,何況人<br />\n你前面同後面都仲有好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f39be728d8d54fa48ac9727950ab143173c527","tid":1474781,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ea08c067580b32fa2171422700cb6a9c10543e3","tid":1474781,"uid":187995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"一開始同幾個朋友一齊踏上旅程<br />\n最初我行得比較慢<br />\n佢哋會等埋我，鼓勵我行快啲<br />\n然後開始有人因為做法唔同而分開行<br />\n我都明白兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n之後我行得比較快，本來想鼓勵佢地<br />\n但佢地話：「你行先啦，我地行唔到咁快。」<br />\n我認為佢地會喺背後支持我，所以獨自行咗一段時間<br />\n我回頭一望，發現佢地叫我自己行個陣已經停低咗<br />\n我大叫，但佢地已被無力感操控，冇辦法再行<br />\n開頭分道揚鑣嘅朋友亦行得越來越遠<br />\n最後我只能一個人行落去<br />\n<br />\n但近期我開始失去動力，開始慢慢行，有停低嘅想法<br />\n<br />\n求鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=144f9cfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"02e9108fc3e6bfa1661257fb655f3247662ef883","tid":1474781,"uid":185057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ea08c067580b32fa2171422700cb6a9c10543e3","tid":1474781,"uid":187995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"一開始同幾個朋友一齊踏上旅程<br />\n最初我行得比較慢<br />\n佢哋會等埋我，鼓勵我行快啲<br />\n然後開始有人因為做法唔同而分開行<br />\n我都明白兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n之後我行得比較快，本來想鼓勵佢地<br />\n但佢地話：「你行先啦，我地行唔到咁快。」<br />\n我認為佢地會喺背後支持我，所以獨自行咗一段時間<br />\n我回頭一望，發現佢地叫我自己行個陣已經停低咗<br />\n我大叫，但佢地已被無力感操控，冇辦法再行<br />\n開頭分道揚鑣嘅朋友亦行得越來越遠<br />\n最後我只能一個人行落去<br />\n<br />\n但近期我開始失去動力，開始慢慢行，有停低嘅想法<br />\n<br />\n求鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:56:58.000Z","msg":"每次想停既時候,黑警做實事都會鼓勵我地出返黎,612,721,811"},{"pid":"7537fb79d96cf6319ce53adfffd5d70838d90836","tid":1474781,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"攰又點？ 唔洗撐呀？<br />\n經歷左咁多 邊個唔攰？<br />\n邊個唔想星期六日係屋企開住冷氣訓晏教？<br />\n我地冇左6條人命 700幾個手足 2隻眼你同我講想放棄？"},{"pid":"e242981e57a2f381988e05b56ad90fc88a68ee0b","tid":1474781,"uid":206203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:00:37.000Z","msg":"覺得辛苦可以休息，可以抽時間做其他嘢，放鬆，冇人會怪你，加油💪<br />\n無論前面有幾難行，都總會有人同你一齊行。<br />\n苦中作樂也未嘗不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98529d50ba0a301813dbee3e419dc6ee2900dcd0","tid":1474781,"uid":207197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YndGq3A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYndGq3A.png&h=6a4cd52c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"796b459e207eb25150ab71e404fd10d35faff974","tid":1474781,"uid":293352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:03:28.000Z","msg":"如果攰就休息一陣，你絕對唔係孤單一個，仲有好多同路人！<br />\n大家一齊撐落去！"},{"pid":"69d70d63eee55542dcab9170fea6d8a3f1e30963","tid":1474781,"uid":225567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"睇少日連登，出街玩下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b5976e8e646d534028d14edd829253c542a952","tid":1474781,"uid":186981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7RtTBPOLLvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7RtTBPOLLvY&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=ac4af911\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7RtTBPOLLvY</a><br />\n唔好忘記死咗𠴱六個兄弟姊妹<br />\n要繼續代替佢哋行落去<br />\n堅持"},{"pid":"a80316db91149b26b1e8653caf13e0d0952e9b4e","tid":1474781,"uid":214276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02585f04d034568cd580a500ea545ef09f418e51","tid":1474781,"uid":307140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:06:11.000Z","msg":"休息一下再繼續上路！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ad580501666d3b0d9165b9b0c3b2ea86b8554b","tid":1474781,"uid":206065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EfuFGD1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEfuFGD1.png&h=774418a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9603fd7d7418c8b97f04fc864569d6846b90d401","tid":1474781,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:09:36.000Z","msg":"放棄咗<br />\n以後你想開始都冇得開始"},{"pid":"01fc8b8f93bebd2dfacad1a00bd84a931a805430","tid":1474781,"uid":194609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:10:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MSFdZD2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMSFdZD2.png&h=bfd387f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們別再犯五年前的錯，好嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1477040\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1477040</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fb9b3c3b1b2b805d5aa3a4caf117b7457f7c08e7","tid":1474781,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:10:44.000Z","msg":"做兩日港豬，調整心情，放遠啲睇，中共內憂外患，腹背受敵，只要我地堅持，我地就會贏。"},{"pid":"589983ef8625ea1ca1502b9b9e11da5ed42b51ad","tid":1474781,"uid":266231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:11:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f569f068a10dc0daf9f772a9c80426dcca802319","tid":1474781,"uid":303911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:15:22.000Z","msg":"我和理非接力，我認醒覺得慢，但係你地令我同朋友走出來，因為有你地一齊行！我身邊已經多左政治冷感人出來！可以失望但唔可以放棄！不絕望！"},{"pid":"16e9f8e51ddfab8bc2524c34648b428e31d125c2","tid":1474781,"uid":303911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HFdCJU2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHFdCJU2.jpg&h=287dfca0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTv9z1K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTv9z1K.jpg&h=c5b8ec4d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}